newsitem.title: EGYPT: Egypt pound overnight, one-week rates little changed.
newsitem.headline: Egypt pound overnight, one-week rates little changed.

text.p: Overnight interbank rates on the Egyptian pound were little changed in the private sector market on Tuesday in a range of 10 to 10-1/4 percent against Monday's range of 10 to 10-3/16, bankers said. One banker quoted a rate of 9-3/4 percent.
One-week rates stood at between 10-1/16 and 10-3/8 percent, against 10-1/4 to 10-3/8 percent on Monday.
Public sector banks maintain their minimum overnight lending rates at 10-1/2 percent.
